msg: The Jena ModelSpec vocabulary as an RDFS vocabulary.

author: chris-dollin
msg: Arranged that Polyadic graphs (in particular, MultiUnions) have
PrefixMappings that are the combination of the PrefixMappings of their
components, with the base graph having master dibs and being the only
target for updates. Also arranged that BaseInfGraphs have the same
PrefixMapping as their raw graphs. Put in some tests for this.
Also arranged that the tmp directory is taken from the system property

author: chris-dollin
msg: Added PolyadicPrefixMappingImpl, to provide an combining-prefix-map for
Polyadic and hence Union, so that (eventually) OntModels will have the
prefixes of the combination of their base and imported models.
